  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SkateLab is a 100% physics-driven skateboarding sandbox built by a skateboarder, for people who love skateboarding.</h2>. . . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/b9a6ba45e0340f4ab2c8eedd0884548a.poster.avif?t=1749912268\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/b9a6ba45e0340f4ab2c8eedd0884548a.webm?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/b9a6ba45e0340f4ab2c8eedd0884548a.mp4?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONTROLS</h2>Starting with a fresh take on dual-stick board control, SkateLab was designed to prioritize responsiveness above anything.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT'S THE MOTIVATION?</h2>For now.. just skate! We're launching into early access as a <i>sandbox</i> where you're likely to get lost in the mechanics of skateboarding. Master the controls and develop a style naturally through your own movement.<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/da142f84fb5381dfd7a945b7adcd3607.avif?t=1749912268\" width=600 height=162 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER FREE-SKATE</h2>Enjoy skating the way you want to, with who you want to - whether that's alone or with friends!<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/479bb796ef4161bbb7b23d9f2d42f822.poster.avif?t=1749912268\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/479bb796ef4161bbb7b23d9f2d42f822.webm?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/479bb796ef4161bbb7b23d9f2d42f822.mp4?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD SPOTS</h2>Use the object-dropper to build and modify your very own skate spots! Move, Rotate, Scale, and even Bend objects for endless possibilities.<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/e6cf12e558aef834a3092a1cf496a5dc.poster.avif?t=1749912268\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/e6cf12e558aef834a3092a1cf496a5dc.webm?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/e6cf12e558aef834a3092a1cf496a5dc.mp4?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPLAYS</h2>Look back at your best tricks! Rewind, play, and record with your favorite screen capturing software!<br><br>. . . .",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SkateLab is a 100% physics-driven skateboarding sandbox built by a skateboarder, for people who love skateboarding.</h2>. . . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/b9a6ba45e0340f4ab2c8eedd0884548a.poster.avif?t=1749912268\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/b9a6ba45e0340f4ab2c8eedd0884548a.webm?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/b9a6ba45e0340f4ab2c8eedd0884548a.mp4?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONTROLS</h2>Starting with a fresh take on dual-stick board control, SkateLab was designed to prioritize responsiveness above anything.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT'S THE MOTIVATION?</h2>For now.. just skate! We're launching into early access as a <i>sandbox</i> where you're likely to get lost in the mechanics of skateboarding. Master the controls and develop a style naturally through your own movement.<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/da142f84fb5381dfd7a945b7adcd3607.avif?t=1749912268\" width=600 height=162 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER FREE-SKATE</h2>Enjoy skating the way you want to, with who you want to - whether that's alone or with friends!<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/479bb796ef4161bbb7b23d9f2d42f822.poster.avif?t=1749912268\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/479bb796ef4161bbb7b23d9f2d42f822.webm?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/479bb796ef4161bbb7b23d9f2d42f822.mp4?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD SPOTS</h2>Use the object-dropper to build and modify your very own skate spots! Move, Rotate, Scale, and even Bend objects for endless possibilities.<br><br>. . . . . .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/e6cf12e558aef834a3092a1cf496a5dc.poster.avif?t=1749912268\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/e6cf12e558aef834a3092a1cf496a5dc.webm?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983940/extras/e6cf12e558aef834a3092a1cf496a5dc.mp4?t=1749912268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPLAYS</h2>Look back at your best tricks! Rewind, play, and record with your favorite screen capturing software!<br><br>. . . .",
